{"tid":1562013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[侵侵縮沙鳥]將會撤消增加５％關稅","createTime":"2019-09-12T00:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:48:49.000Z","uid":100581,"like":26,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a28ff53274e32365f0da3548dcd36e428064df","tid":1562013,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:12:25.000Z","msg":"為慶祝你地國慶，美國宣佈撤消增加５％關稅<br />\n<strong>Trump Delays China Tariff Increase by Two Weeks, Until Oct. 15</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-09-11/trump-delays-china-tariff-increase-by-two-weeks-until-oct-15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-09-11%2Ftrump-delays-china-tariff-increase-by-two-weeks-until-oct-15&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=20acb8ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-09-11/trump-delays-china-tariff-increase-by-two-weeks-until-oct-15</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n２個禮拜咁多啦！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cb63684e3440fcfbeedfc1f6ed72fec5df8e1d7d","tid":1562013,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:12:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c66673b248aa54d4706eab45114ccc2b38d0d750","tid":1562013,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f8f3eef7a94956a08ab50472bdf1701f4ac31e9","tid":1562013,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"President Donald Trump on Wednesday said he was moving back a 5% increase in tariffs on Chinese goods by two weeks -- out of respect for the celebration of the 70th anniversary of the revolution that brought the communist government to power.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;At the request of the Vice Premier of China, Liu He, and due to the fact that the People&rsquo;s Republic of China will be celebrating their 70th Anniversary on October 1st, we have agreed, as a gesture of good will, to move the increased Tariffs on 250 Billion Dollars worth of goods (25% to 30%), from October 1st to October 15th,&rdquo; Trump wrote on Twitter."},{"pid":"02308a10ecee0ea7d93141c71c93269adecf8cd8","tid":1562013,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:14:18.000Z","msg":"Both China and the U.S. have seen signs that the trade conflict between the two countries is taking an economic toll.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier on Wednesday, China announced a range of U.S. goods to be exempted from 25% extra tariffs put in place last year, as the government seeks to ease the impact from the trade war.<br />\n<br />\nTrump escalated the U.S.-China trade war in August when he announced an increase in the levy, already in effect, on $250 billion in Chinese goods to 30% from 25% starting Oct. 1.<br />\n<br />\nThe nations are scheduled to hold two rounds of face-to-face negotiations in Washington in coming weeks with the first this month and the second in early October with a visit from He."},{"pid":"51a633b2abe583efec8227056a92d6ddd6bc1419","tid":1562013,"uid":125869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:15:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Until Oct. 15</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c662867599c9683a56b579fde4ec74d4bb5ed0ec","tid":1562013,"uid":100581,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51a633b2abe583efec8227056a92d6ddd6bc1419","tid":1562013,"uid":125869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:15:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Until Oct. 15</span></strong></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:16:38.000Z","msg":"話係慶祝你地國慶。<br />\n<br />\n查實定係囉景"},{"pid":"2f6140c2cfe7e195e50771ed01c844c14138c0dd","tid":1562013,"uid":15943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"Delay 唔係 withdraw <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c14e400191f9008b2099128f503de327cbcd6d7","tid":1562013,"uid":37443,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:17:24.000Z","msg":"Delay<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31c7e9d4eaaaa7ec53ed973ded0b8820183f743","tid":1562013,"uid":141268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"f40e7c6689525e53f693d82a36381d68a14c3c22","tid":1562013,"uid":274722,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:18:23.000Z","msg":"the tax is dead"},{"pid":"ba233fba762e998600f0ef58fd6b92fee27e65b2","tid":1562013,"uid":38572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:18:53.000Z","msg":"再嘈加多10％"},{"pid":"73bd12dfceec45485d22dec8c14cb3c9f4d9c930","tid":1562013,"uid":4783,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:19:27.000Z","msg":"fake news<br />\nblocked不推文"},{"pid":"67a6a5983f1a2a7c3086125dc939e76f7fba537d","tid":1562013,"uid":